Assistive Technology:
====================

	Practical tool that can enable people with disabilities and older people to maximise their independence.

	eg: screen reading software
inde
	So This s/w helps in students/employees to directly apply for assitive funding for themselves


Requirements:
============

	-> User logs in to application and background check will be done on user regarding their disability if they are true an account will be created by giving them alert in email or something.

	


